OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thu 9 Apr to Sat 18 Apr
OL,6,FRather changeable conditions are
OL,7,Fexpected through this period, as
OL,8,FAtlantic frontal systems track
OL,9,Feastwards across the UK, accompanied
OL,10,Fby some strong winds at times. These
OL,11,Fwill bring occasional spells of rain
OL,12,For showers, heaviest and most frequent
OL,13,Fin the west and northwest, with longer
OL,14,Fdrier interludes likely in the south
OL,15,Fand sheltered eastern areas. Whilst
OL,16,Ftemperatures will be close to average
OL,17,Ffor the period as a whole, there may
OL,18,Fbe opportunities for some short-lived
OL,19,Fwarm spells in the south and east.
OL,20,FConversely, occasional colder
OL,21,Finterludes in the northwest will bring
OL,22,Fthe chance of some wintry showers,
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,23,Fespecially over hills, and overnight
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
OL,24,Ffrost.
