OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sat 18 Apr to Sat 2 MayFIt
OL,6,Fis probable that more blocked, or at
OL,7,Fleast slowly evolving, weather
OL,8,Fpatterns will become increasingly
OL,9,Fdominant through the middle of the
OL,10,Fmonth. Whilst confidence is low, this
OL,11,Fmay result in more settled and drier
OL,12,Fconditions overall. There may,
OL,13,Fhowever, still be some more unsettled
OL,14,Finterludes at times, especially in the
OL,15,Fsouth and southwest. Temperatures will
OL,16,Fprobably be around or a little above
OL,17,Fnormal for the period as a whole, and
OL,18,Fits possible we may see some
OL,19,Fpleasantly warm spring weather at
OL,20,Ftimes.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
